  1. Define which columns are relevant. The relevant columns will be used to create a concise table for subsequent analysis. Note: Subid is not needed, because the leap-q files contain a uniform_id, which acts as a key. Only ee.xlsx does not have a uniform_id -> needs further preprocessing.
